OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FImpact of night work needs 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmore research - mayor      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More research needs to be done on the  
OL,6, effect working at night has on people's
OL,7, health, the mayor of London said.      
OL,9,FSadiq Kahn and the capital's night czar
OL,10,FAmy Lame heard of health issues faced  
OL,11,Fby night workers during a wellbeing    
OL,12,Fevent held in Vauxhall on Thursday.    
OL,14,FThe mayor called for the government to 
OL,15,Frecognise the "distinct needs of night 
OL,16,Fworkers", with his office saying 1.3m  
OL,17,Fpeople work between 18:00 and 06:00.   
OL,19,FThe government said there were         
OL,20,Fprotections in place for night workers.
